## Local-only V1/V2 design experiment (do not commit)
##
## All redesign work — V2 pages, dev shells, the toggle, and helpers — lives
## under `panel/src/_dev-redesign/`. The 5 modified dispatcher entry points
## (DiagnosticsPage.tsx, Players/PlayersPage.tsx, Settings/SettingsPage.tsx,
## Settings/SettingsCardShell.tsx, Settings/settingsItems.tsx) are kept out
## of pushes via `git update-index --skip-worktree`.
##
panel/src/_dev-redesign/

.reports/*
license_report/*
.tsc/*
*.ignore.*
/start_*.bat
monitor-*.zip
bundle_size_report.html
.github/.cienv
scripts/**/*.local.*
.runtime/
.vscode/
*.tsbuildinfo
.npm-upgrade.json
.github/agents/*
.cursor/*
!.cursor/rules/
!.cursor/rules/**
!.cursor/skills/
!.cursor/skills/**
.claude/

